94
00:13:57,400 --> 00:14:01,820
I was drinking some alcohol.

95
00:14:02,810 --> 00:14:11,080
-What about now? The sleeping pattern is it better?

96
00:14:11,320 --> 00:14:17,550
-After 6-7 weeks it got a little better but the restlessness is there

97
00:14:17,650 --> 00:14:22,900
and I’ve been having so many nightmares.

98
00:14:25,410 --> 00:14:31,740
