106
00:15:20,590 --> 00:15:29,010
-No, this fatigue makes me not able to do anything, so it’s like throwing my life away.

107
00:15:32,260 --> 00:15:36,250
-But why do you have guilt feelings? Because you are fatigued?

108
00:15:36,350 --> 00:15:37,990
-Yes.

109
00:15:38,090 --> 00:15:44,380
-Are you sure?
