128
00:17:56,410 --> 00:18:02,770
-Yes and I try everything to escape, I wake up screaming no, no, no and throwing

129
00:18:02,870 --> 00:18:09,160
with a terrible pain in my neck and I have a headache from that.

130
00:18:09,740 --> 00:18:17,070
-Do you remember scenes from childhood or you have suppressed them?

131
00:18:17,170 --> 00:18:26,770
-I don’t remember anything from my childhood, everything is black up to 15-16 and

132
00:18:26,870 --> 00:18:33,360
