167
00:23:23,110 --> 00:23:27,830
-But now it’s not so strong anymore this sensitivity.

168
00:23:27,930 --> 00:23:34,330
-It’s there but it’s not this compulsiveness and the same with this despair I have

169
00:23:34,430 --> 00:23:42,430
with this religious. It was very strong for some weeks but now it faded, so now it’s better.

170
00:23:58,940 --> 00:24:00,940
I sensed that I had more fears.

171
00:24:06,450 --> 00:24:09,580
-What kind?
