179
00:25:03,690 --> 00:25:06,610
-Did you swim while you are here, did you swim at all?

180
00:25:06,710 --> 00:25:21,310
-Very fast, just once a little bit. I love the sea, I want to dive but I’m afraid to go underneath

181
00:25:21,410 --> 00:25:23,860
because I don’t feel that I can breathe.

182
00:25:43,360 --> 00:25:54,250
I think that’s it. Another thing I didn’t mention last time, it has become a little stronger.

183
00:25:56,940 --> 00:26:05,690
