185
00:26:13,360 --> 00:26:25,200
It’s like a lot of blood in the head and dizziness and disturbed vision and I have to stop.

186
00:26:27,460 --> 00:26:33,380
I can hear the pulse and palpitation in the ear, very exhausted.

187
