00:28:21,570 --> 00:28:25,950
-If you take only sugar. Other sweets do you take?

199
00:28:26,050 --> 00:28:28,550
Chocolates?
-Yes.

200
00:28:29,300 --> 00:28:33,630
-No reaction?
