202
00:28:40,710 --> 00:28:47,800
-No, I don’t remember I told you but yes that is true, I can have that.

203
00:28:56,040 --> 00:29:01,950
I’m much better in fresh air, I can not stand stuffy rooms, the feeling

204
00:29:02,050 --> 00:29:18,450
of not having enough oxygen… but I don’t think I told you so much last time

205
00:29:18,550 --> 00:29:32,530
about I had an injury in my head and the whole spine in 1985 and I fell down 2,5 meters

206
00:29:32,630 --> 00:29:37,700
on rocks and I hit my head and the spine.

207
00:29:37,800 --> 00:29:40,890
-You were in the hospital?
-No.

208
00:29:41,880 --> 00:29:44,370
-You took no medicines?

209
00:29:44,470 --> 00:29:49,120
